	<entry name="tzeguard/Cult" value="Cult of Tzeentch"/>
	<entry name="tzeguard/CultDescription" value="Building that produces special Chaos units and increases loyalty."/>
	<entry name="tzeguard/CultFlavor" value="What are gods without followers? Here, Cultists and Dark Apostles alike plot to bring converts to the worship of Chaos—not a hard task on Gladius, once people see the inhuman Xenos, the undoubted effects of Khorne power, and the Daemonic shapes lingering in the chancel."/>
